By the Law of Cosines on triangle $ABC,$
\[\cos B = \frac{9 + \frac{81}{2} - 36}{2 \cdot 3\cdot \frac{9}{\sqrt{2}}} = \frac{\sqrt{2}}{4}.\]Then by the Law of Cosines on triangle $ABD,$
